{"tid":436600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣都比較內向","createTime":"2017-10-15T09:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T01:59:21.000Z","uid":26122,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc9fd4139c49cad5239581fcabb2f9fb53fe70f","tid":436600,"uid":26122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"成日好羨慕啲外向嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一開始識新朋友既都可以搵到話題好似識咗好耐咁<br />\n睇翻自己 對住啲啱啱識嘅人就算不斷9up大家共同嘅興趣都淨係認真去討論 唔太識講笑 好怕自己講錯野 比咗個壞印象人地<br />\n好想同佢傾多啲 但硬係怕羞 一直淨係做緊普通朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想外向啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cc3d2dbd4a8d4a8b1527c9b1cd5c7bd7e4fc64","tid":436600,"uid":89709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"社交能力有問題"},{"pid":"26d91cf72ef112f39c578fc1e1e74ef659ac3e9c","tid":436600,"uid":67289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"毒撚"},{"pid":"0784e6bbb4c193401bbcc38f7b2066ce5819cbae","tid":436600,"uid":92499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:33:28.000Z","msg":"我....<br />\n家下份工返左3個月左右<br />\n平時見到撞到,聲都唔會打<br />\n25A0冇朋友"},{"pid":"dc174e868610db971985acbc8362dea698acaf19","tid":436600,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔都係"},{"pid":"3211b5fa60f9edf62a949d5467c61f0338bafa25","tid":436600,"uid":26122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社交能力有問題</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時想自己一個多啲"},{"pid":"2f59286e0a7cc07a3b431b259e335fa0f1a333ad","tid":436600,"uid":26122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚</blockquote><br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"